reviews.text: I had an interesting ginger/honey iced coffee. Cakes looked good, although I didn't have one. No soft drinks available. Free WiFi, staff are friendly and helpful and the toilets are pretty clean.
One of my favorite while studying abroad. People are so nice and coffee is delicious.
A very relaxing place in a very busy area. Good food and beverages. The portion that they serve is amazing.
Nice coffee and place to long stay in weekend. Breakfast set( before 11:30 AM) is highly recommended.
It’s comfortable place in Jordan, the cafe has their own coffee machine and offer meal like pasta, I tried White Flat and it’s good texture :)
